# SCv5 documentation

When editing files under `docs/`:

- Follow **`docs/spec/atomic-documentation.md`** (atomic notes, `00-index.md` hubs, relative links only — no wikilinks as canonical).
- After adding/removing/renaming doc files in a pack, update that pack’s **`00-index.md`**.
- Prefer linking to the **canonical** atom for a fact; avoid duplicating long passages across files.
- For methodology details, see **`docs/spec/00-index.md`**.

Project-wide agent context: **`AGENTS.md`**.
